for what he's done.

00:59.624 --> 01:01.844
I didn't mean to hurt you.
I love you, all right?

01:01.974 --> 01:04.107
Don't worry.
I'm gonna get you out.

01:04.238 --> 01:06.544
Sister Elise,
will you marry me?

01:06.675 --> 01:09.547
